# What is a 'token' in an LLM?

- In the context of LLMs it references a unit of text that is used in LLM request and responses.
- It is vital in determining usage as well as charging for the service usage.

# Creating a Subscription

- Vital when using ChatGPT at the API layer.
- You must have 'credit' associated with your openai account - all set via the billing interface.

# API - Pricing

- Different GPT models have different pricing structures.

# GET the API key

- API keys are unique and tied directly to your account.

# APIs and Endpoints

- openai > Settings > Documentation > API Reference documentation provides the relevant endpoints.

# Create the API Request

- openai > Settings > Documentation > Quick Start tutorial provides relevant documentation.

# Warning

All of the above will be subject to change.
